_sText:
Locate fy_heavyhouse located in the ZIP/WINRAR folder
Extract fy_heavyhouse into your counterstrike source maps folder

EXAMPLE: C:/ Program Files / Steam /SteamApps/ *account name* /counter-strike source /cstrike/maps

Run Css and play the map



This is an inside map, a basic T vs CT map.
You are equipped with 
-Machine Gun (M249-PARA)
-Dual Pistols (elites)
-Knife

Although the map is small it is impossible to camp because you can see and shoot into each room using the windows provided.
